x\" \/><\/a><\/div>\n<div style=\"width: 25%; padding: 10px; float: left; text-align: center; border: 1px solid #E9E9E9; background: #fff;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/ui-ux-development.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-9147\" src=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/hire-uiux-designer.png\" alt=\"Hire Remote UI\/UX Designer\" width=\"177\" height=\"177\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/hire-uiux-designer.png 177w, https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/hire-uiux-designer-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 177px) 100vw, 177px\" \/><\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Our_Hire_Remote_Developers_Models\"><\/span><a id=\"hire-remote-developers-models\"><\/a>Our Hire Remote Developers Models<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Regardless of the business size or complexity of the project, hiring professional developers is a crucial task. It is essential to know the different hiring models and select the model which meets your needs. Each model comes with pros and cons. Understand different hiring models and know which could be the best for your enterprise.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Managed_Team\"><\/span>Managed Team<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>In this model, Gozoom Technologies takes complete responsibility for your app development needs. This model allows business owners to focus on the strategic activities of a growing business, soaring to new heights of success. Our software developers will be accountable for all your project needs.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Client_Managed_Team\"><\/span>Client Managed Team<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>In this model, our dedicated development team will seamlessly collaborate with an in-house team or project managers. Our dedicated offshore development team will act as a natural progression or extension of your team, providing critical support to your in-house team.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Hybrid_Model\"><\/span>Hybrid Model<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>The hybrid model provides the much-needed flexibility in deploying part of your team on-site while the rest of your team works from an offshore location.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Before_hiring_remote_developers_you_should_know_little_about_remote_developers_and_their_types\"><\/span>Before hiring remote developers you should know little about remote developers and their types.<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Who_are_remote_developers\"><\/span>Who are remote developers?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Remote developers are dedicated developers who work for your company from a remote location. They are outsourced assets that are working from different locations. As the working methodology is shifting it is necessary to hire remote developers. Let us dive into the types of remote developers before you hire a remote developer for your brand.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Dedicated_developer\"><\/span>Dedicated developer<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Remote dedicated developers are developers who work for your company\u2019s project and can be bound using outsourcing contracts. They work full-time on the project and have to fulfill certain requirements that are given by the company with which they are associated. The company has full control over the work of the developers. With these developers, you get 100% commitment and maximum security with your confidential information of the project.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Extension_developers\"><\/span>Extension developers<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Sometimes, companies hire remote developers as an extension to their in-house teams to bridge the technology gap as it cant be fulfilled in their local regions. The technology expert will associate with your in-house team to offer his\/her expertise on the project and enhance the performance.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Freelancers\"><\/span>Freelancers<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>When there are some minor projects, then companies prefer to hire freelancers to fulfill the requirements. The requirements for these projects are pre-defined so companies know what they are looking for when they hire freelancers. The freelancer works on different projects and have a wide skill set. Besides bringing a new pool of skill-set, the hiring process for the company is easier and they have to invest less money. However, if freelances offer a broad skill-set then they also expect flexibility in the timing of their work. So, companies have to give them their freedom in pace and timings when they hire them for a certain project.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"IT_Staff_Augmentation\"><\/span>IT Staff Augmentation<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>This is another way to hire remote developers and fill the technology gap for the companies. You can opt for a small staffing agency, recruitment agency, or traditional staff provider to fulfill your needs. However, this method is not budget-friendly in the long run and you may experience a lack of dedication in the staff due to the hiring model.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Steps_to_Hire_Remote_Developers\"><\/span><a id=\"steps-to-hire-remote-developers\"><\/a>Steps to Hire Remote Developers<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-9145\" src=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/steps-to-hire-remote-developers.png\" alt=\"Steps to Hire Remote Developers\" width=\"908\" height=\"200\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/steps-to-hire-remote-developers.png 908w, https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/steps-to-hire-remote-developers-300x66.png 300w, https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/steps-to-hire-remote-developers-768x169.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 908px) 100vw, 908px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>How to hire remote developers? If you are stressed with this issue then Gozoom Technologies is here to the rescue. Hiring web &amp; mobile app developers from Gozoom Technologies is an easy process. Here is how to hire expert developers for your project.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Drop an Inquiry:<\/strong> Simply send us an inquiry, providing information about your web development or mobile app development project, as well as your objectives.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Consult With Our Experts:<\/strong> Our business analyst will provide technical feasibility and analysis of your project.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Select Engagement Model:<\/strong> Based on your budget, business needs, and technical assessment, you can select an engagement model that meets your needs.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Sign Off and Begin Work:<\/strong> Sign the agreement and your dedicated developer begins work on your web development or mobile app development project.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Scale Your Team:<\/strong> Expand your team based on your development needs.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Final_tips\"><\/span>Final tips<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Whether you are looking to hire a developer for a short-term project or a dedicated development team for a long-term project, it is important to create a cohesive and inclusive work environment for remote developers.<\/p>\n<p>Remember, they are a strategic asset to achieve your business objective. Keeping your priorities and project roadmap clear will play an instrumental role in a successful partnership.<\/p>\n<p>Ensure that remote developers don&#8217;t work in silos, rather they should have a clear understanding of your strategy and their role to make things work. Partner with a reliable web &amp; mobile app development company with a talent pool of professional developers for your project.<\/p>\n<p>You will be able to compare different answers and understand different outlooks, giving you a better perspective to <a href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/hire-dedicated-developers.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">hire dedicated developers<\/a>. It is important to share concerns about potential problems to manage in the future through collaboration.<\/p>\n<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_47_1 ez-toc-wrap-left counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-transparent ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">Table of Contents<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 ' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/hire-remote-developers-for-your-web-mobile-app-development-project.html\/#Hire_Remote_App_Developers\" title=\"Hire Remote App Developers\">Hire Remote App Developers<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/hire-remote-developers-for-your-web-mobile-app-development-project.html\/#Here_are_Advantages_to_Hire_Remote_Developers_for_Your_Project\" title=\"Here are Advantages to Hire Remote Developers for Your Project\">Here are Advantages to Hire Remote Developers for Your Project<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3'><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/hire-remote-developers-for-your-